snippet.title: Try Google's most powerful AI model Gemini 3 Pro in Copilot today
snippet.description:
Google just shook up the leaderboard with Gemini 3 Pro, their most powerful AI model yet. It's built not just to pass tests, but to plan, act, and orchestrate multi-step tasks. And the best part? You can try it today directly within GitHub Copilot with your Pro subscription.

#Google #Gemini #Copilot

About GitHub
It’s where over 180 million developers create, share, and ship the best code possible. It’s a place for anyone, from anywhere, to build anything—it’s where the world builds software. https://github.com
